        <![CDATA[<div class="alert alert-info" role="alert"><button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-hidden="true">×</button>
        <h3>Popup System Messages - Atom for Gantry Framework</h3>
        <span aria-hidden="true" class="icon-user"></span>&nbsp;<em>Andreas Kar (andreas.kar@gmx.at)</em>
        <p><b>INFO</b>:&nbsp;Dieses Atom wurde für Gantry Helium installiert.<br />Wenn Sie das Atom für ein anderes Gantry Template installieren möchten, dann müssen die Dateien wie folgt platziert werden:</p>
        <ul><li><code>*.yaml</code> =&gt; <code>/templates/[TEMPLATE]/custom/particles</code></li><li><code>*.twig</code> =&gt; <code>/templates/[TEMPLATE]/custom/particles</code></li><li><code>*.js</code> =&gt; <code>/templates/[TEMPLATE]/custom/js</code></li><li><code>*.scss</code> =&gt; <code>/templates/[TEMPLATE]/custom/scss</code></li></ul>
        <div>Repository: <a href="https://git.io/fjrNR" title="Github Repository" target="_blank">https://git.io/fjrNR</a></div>
        <div>Website: <a href="https://gantryprojects.com" title="Gantry Projects Website" target="_blank">https://gantryprojects.com</a></div></div>]]>
    </description>
    <fileset>
        <files folder="particles" target="templates/g5_helium/custom/particles">
            <filename>popup-system-messages.html.twig</filename>
            <filename>popup-system-messages.yaml</filename>
        </files>
        <files folder="scss" target="templates/g5_helium/custom/scss">
            <filename>_popup-system-messages.scss</filename>
        </files>
        <files folder="js" target="templates/g5_helium/custom/js">
            <filename>popup-system-messages.js</filename>
            <filename>popup-system-messages.min.js</filename>
        </files>
    </fileset>
</extension>